{"tid":1802355,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"若學校不配合教育局調查黃師 楊潤雄指認為校長已不能勝任，局方有權取消其校長資格","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T11:13:58.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b59d539e8ccd7dc6700a861e1c1f655c3837f4a1","tid":1802355,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374877&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK97%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=0dbeaf86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374877&h=c6af1d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374877</a><br />\nNow新聞台】教育局局長楊潤雄接受內地《上觀新聞》專訪被問到若果要求學校對教師進行調查，學校不配合調查，甚至校長也支持教師行為，教育局如何應對，楊潤雄指若認為校長已不能勝任，局方有權取消其校長資格。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄指學校的基本態度是怎樣，是否支持教師，其實很容易看出來，例如學校認為教師「沒有問題」，局方就知道學校、校長的態度和立場可能「有問題」，便會從管理角度去處理，因為校長是由教育局常任秘書長委任，如果局方覺得一個校長已經不能勝任，可以取消校長資格，如果情節嚴重，連當一個教師也不合適還可以取消他的教師資格，如果程度不嚴重會建議辦學團體、校董共同幫助校長做好工作，局方亦有權直接委任校董加入學校的校董委員會，參與學校日常管理。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞"},{"pid":"cb8409a3ec9334f929c38fef9467406e261c8d6a","tid":1802355,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位黎用下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由窮爸爸富爸爸探討黃色經濟圈發展</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>黃色證券圈</strong></span></sp